HEADWORD: Cispadane
<hw>Cis"pa*dane`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>cis-</ets> + L. <ets>Padanus</ets>, pert. to the <ets>Padus</ets>
